---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/ui/Container.astro";
import Subheading from "../../components/ui/Subheading.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="User Onboarding - Lunogram"
  description="Turn signups into active users. Guide new customers to their first value moment with targeted welcome sequences across email, push, and in-app messages."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-24">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <a href="/use-cases" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white/70 transition-colors mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
          All use cases
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-green-500/15 ring-1 ring-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 01-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 01.06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 00-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 004.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <Subheading class="text-green-400 mb-4">Onboarding</Subheading>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white text-balance">
          Turn signups into<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          active users
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Most users who sign up never come back. Lunogram helps you guide them to their first value moment with targeted, multi-channel welcome sequences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          The problem with most onboarding
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          You spend time and money acquiring users, but most of them drop off before experiencing the value your product offers. A generic "welcome" email isn't enough. Users need guidance tailored to who they are, what they're trying to do, and where they are in the process.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-red-500/20 mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">One-size-fits-all</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/50">Same email for every user regardless of their role, plan, or intent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-red-500/20 mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Wrong timing</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/50">Messages sent on a fixed schedule instead of reacting to user behavior.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-red-500/20 mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M9.88 9.88l-3.29-3.29m7.532 7.532l3.29 3.29M3 3l3.59 3.59m0 0A9.953 9.953 0 0112 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.543 7a10.025 10.025 0 01-4.132 5.411m0 0L21 21"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">No visibility</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/50">No way to see who's stuck, who's progressing, or where users drop off.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- How Lunogram Helps -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-green-400 uppercase mb-4">
          How Lunogram helps
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-12">
          Behavior-driven onboarding that adapts
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-green-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Segment users from day one</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Use signup properties, referral source, or plan type to route users into the right onboarding track. A developer gets a different journey than a marketing manager.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-green-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">React to behavior, not schedules</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Trigger the next message when a user completes a step — or nudge them if they haven't. Lunogram's journey builder lets you branch on any event or property.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-green-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Reach users on the right channel</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Some users check email, others respond to push notifications. Orchestrate across email, SMS, push, and webhooks from a single journey — and let the data tell you what works.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-green-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Iterate with experiments</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                A/B test subject lines, send times, and entire journey branches. Find what converts trial users into paying customers and double down.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- Example Journey -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-10">
          Example: SaaS trial onboarding
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-white/[0.02] rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 ring-1 ring-white/[0.06]">
          <!-- Trigger -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-green-500/15 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-green-500/25 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] font-medium text-white">User signs up</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-green-400/70 font-mono uppercase bg-green-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full ring-1 ring-green-500/20">trigger</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Send email -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Send welcome email with quick-start guide</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">send</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Wait -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Wait 24 hours</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">delay</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Condition -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 rotate-45 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40 -rotate-45" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Has user completed setup?</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">condition</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Branch outcomes -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-4 bg-white/5"></div>
          <div class="ml-6 sm:ml-10 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-white/[0.04] rounded-xl p-4 ring-1 ring-white/[0.08]">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/70">Yes</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Send "Congrats" email + feature tips for their plan</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/[0.04] rounded-xl p-4 ring-1 ring-white/[0.08]">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-red-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-red-400/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/70">No</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Send helpful nudge with setup guide + offer assistance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Stop losing users after signup
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
          Build onboarding journeys that adapt to each user. Get started in minutes with Lunogram Cloud.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="https://accounts.lunogram.com"
            class="inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-purple-600 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg shadow-violet-500/25 hover:from-violet-500 hover:to-purple-500 transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Get Started
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/use-cases"
            class="inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-white ring-1 ring-white/15 transition-colors hover:bg-white/15"
          >
            View all use cases
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</Layout>
